***WED March 16 -CTMatch.com SPEED Match Dating AGES 35-55 and AFTERPARTY at KOJI 182 Temple Street New Haven, CT

CTMatch.com Hosts The BIGGEST Speed Dating Events in Connecticut – So You Meet More People For The Same Price As A Smaller Speed Dating Event!

Meet MORE Singles FACE to FACE – And Then Pick Your Matches!

SPEED Match Dating lets you meet more Single people in one exciting evening than most people will meet in a whole year!

Meet More People at the Largest Speed Dating Events in Connecticut

SPEED Match Dating lets you Meet MORE Local Singles and Potential Matches In One Exciting Evening at Connecticut’s BIGGEST Speed Dating Events - Meet Someone Special and Party with CTMatch.com

SPEED Match Dating is inexpensive and fun way for busy people looking to meet other local singles. It gives you instant mini dates to help you find that special someone that you will enjoy spending time with and share common interests.

Instead of boring and frustrating dates with people you have little in common with, find someone who matches up with you, your interests and lifestyle, and then build a great relationship!

Your Match results will be emailed to you after the event

All your information is confidential - Unlike other events, we do not share your phone number or personal info

Registration and Appetizers start at 6:30 pm - SPEED Match Dating starts at 7 pm

 

Advance Tickets are $30 - Tickets at the event are $40 if space is available
* Includes Appetizers *

Koji 182
Temple Street
New Haven, CT 06510

Visit www.CTMatch.com or call (860) 236-3343 for more info

 

Check us out in the Hartford Courant -

 http://www.courant.com/features/hc-speed-dating-whole-foods-0601-20100601,0,6776556.story
